    <item>
      <title>股市下跌，财报季全面到来：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们对大量企业盈利报告感到厌倦，股市下跌，而对美联储降息幅度较小的押注继续推高债券收益率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 22:29:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度取消白米出口底价以吸引买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/india-scraps-tax-on-some-rice-exports-to-boost-competitiveness</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度放宽了大米出口仅存的几个限制之一，此举可能有助于承运商在全球市场上削弱竞争对手，并帮助当地种植者以更高的价格出售其作物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/india-scraps-tax-on-some-rice-exports-to-boost-competitiveness</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 18:43:20 GMT</pubDate>
